---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="성명학 | 준비중 | ManyTool"
  description="ManyTool 성명학 페이지는 준비중입니다."
  canonical="https://manytool.net/seongmyeonghak"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-[#121212] px-4 py-20 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-[32px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#e9c349]">Coming Soon</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight">성명학 준비중</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-white/65">
        성명학 기능은 아직 준비중입니다. 추후 이름 구조, 음양 조합, 한글/한자 흐름을 참고형 리포트로 제공할 예정입니다.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="/ai-manseryeok" class="rounded-full bg-[#e9c349] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-black text-[#3c2f00]">사주 리포트로 돌아가기</a>
        <a href="/" class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-black text-white/80">홈으로</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
